# Shared components

- Prefer existing primitives in `components/ui/` and layout pieces in `components/layout/`.
- New reusable chrome (e.g. branch switcher) belongs in `components/layout/` as a named component, not inlined in a single page.
- Do not duplicate sidebar, dropdown, or dialog patterns — extend shared building blocks.
- Use the same UX labels across platforms where the same concept appears (e.g. **Branch** for city sub-accounts).
